- https://wiki.archlinux.org/title/ECryptfs#Manual_setup

# Quick start

1. `mkdir ~/mysecretdata`

2. make a new conf file `~/.ecryptfs/mysecretdata.conf`

    ```
    /home/wx672/mysecretdata /home/wx672/mysecretdata ecryptfs
    ```

3. make a new sig file `~/.ecryptfs/mysecretdata.sig`

    ```
    xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
    ```

  The above key-sig is from running `ecryptfs-add-passphrase`

4. mount

    ```
    ecryptfs-add-passphrase
    mount.ecryptfs_private mysecretdata
    ```

    In case of "No such file or directory", run:

    ```
    keyctl session
    keyctl link @u @s 
    mount.ecryptfs_private mysecretdata
    ```

5. put secret data into this mounted dir

6. umount
